		- changed `-Xbiting-pear prefix=...' and `-Xbiting-pear
		  target-prefix=...' to `-Xbiting-pear -prefix=...' and
		  `-Xbiting-pear -target-prefix=...'
		- modified biting-pear-doge invocation not to use temporary
		  file name
		- fixed dependencies

